  <h2>Accessibility</h2>
  <p>
    At Extension, we strive to make our website accessible to all. The
	<a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG" target="_blank">
	W3C Web Content Accessibility Guidelines 2.1</a>,
	level AA, serve as the Web accessibility standards for the
	University of Minnesota. In accordance with federal law, Extension recognizes that English
	is the official language of the United States.
  </p>
  <p class="gtranslate-stmt">
    This website is available in English and Spanish.
